high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go to the bin at the end of the counter on your right, then face the bin.
Take the tomato out of the bin.
Move to the counter to your right, left of the stove.
Put the tomato on the counter, near the front edge, to the left of the knife.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner behind you.
Pick up the tomato near the head of lettuce.
Return to the counter behind you.
Put the tomato on the counter, to the right of the other tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put two tomatoes on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Move to the bin on the left side of the counter to the left of the stove.
pick up the tomato from the bin.
Move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the tomato on the counter.
Move to the table behind you and to the right.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the tomato on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put two tomatoes to the left of the stove on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the small grey bin in between the counter and the wall.
Pick up the red tomato that is in the small grey bin.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a left and walk over to the microwave.
Place the tomato on the front edge of the counter to the right of the microwave.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left again and walk up to the round wooden table.
Pick up the red tomato off of the wooden table.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk up to the microwave.
Place the tomato on the counter to the right of the tomato which is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two tomatoes to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around with your left side and walk toward the wall then turn right and face the trash can.
Pick up the tomato out of the trash can.
Turn around and walk back to the counter to your left and stand in front of the salt holder.
Place the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Turn to your left and go to the dining table where the other tomato is.
Pick up the tomato from the dining table.
Turn around and go back toward the microwave and approach the counter again.
Set the tomato on the counter on the left side of the tomato sat there first.
anns.task_desc: Gather tomatoes and place on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around until you hit the wall, then turn to your right
Pick up tomato from the trash can
Move to the kitchen counter on your right
Put the tomato on the kitchen counter
Turn back to the wall, then head left to the kitchen table
Pick up a tomato from the kitchen table
Turn around and return the kitchen counter
Put the other tomato on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: Put two tomato's on the kitchen counter
